          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " Because of the extreme interest in this car, we wanted to give an update that it sold for a final hammer price of $758,500 during the RM Sotheby's Amelia Island auction.",
